00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:14,000
 He says in verse 16,

562
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:17,000
 "For how shall it be known that I have found favor in your sight,

563
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:19,000
 I in your people?

564
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:21,000
 Is it not in your going with us that we are distinct,

565
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:24,000
 I in your people, from every other people on the face of the earth?"

566
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:27,000
 So let me just talk to the believers in this room for a moment.

