00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:24,000
 or I'm a part of no denomination.

588
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:28,000
 It's not I read the ESV or you read the NASV, which version is correct.

589
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:31,000
 It's not that you're pro-Trump or anti-Trump.

590
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:35,000
 Like all of the ways that we love to self-identify when it comes to our faith

